---
title: Carb Smart Savoury and Spicy Chicken Lettuce Wraps with Pickled Radishes and Cashews
description: Lettuce wraps are the perfect vessels for delivering maximum flavour. Fast-cooking ground chicken is tossed in a gingery, savoury sauce, then paired with tangy pickled radishes and crunchy cashews for the ultimate balanced bite.
